The additional emails are available in `hs_additional_emails`, so you should be able to add a second filterGroup with:
```{
   filters: [
      {
         operator: 'CONTAINS_TOKEN',
         propertyName: 'hs_additional_emails',
         value: email
      }
   ]
}```
Make sure you put it in a separate filterGroup, not just another filter in the existing group (because you want a logical "or" between them).
